{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-npmpage-js","path":"/npm/packages/zim-gamshooks/","result":{"data":{"npmPackage":{"name":"zim-gamshooks","slug":"/packages/zim-gamshooks/","readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"zim-gams-hooks\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#zim-gams-hooks\" aria-label=\"zim gams hooks permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ZIM GAMS Hooks</h1>\n<h2 id=\"short-description\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#short-description\" aria-label=\"short description permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Short Description</h2>\n<p>Hooks for simplifying usage with GAMS.</p>\n<h2 id=\"demos--examples\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#demos--examples\" aria-label=\"demos  examples permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Demos &#x26; Examples</h2>\n<h3 id=\"usejsglobal-and-usedatastream-basic-communication-with-gams\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#usejsglobal-and-usedatastream-basic-communication-with-gams\" aria-label=\"usejsglobal and usedatastream basic communication with gams permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useJsGlobal and useDatastream (Basic communication with GAMS)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>useJsGlobal</strong> will check for an object with <strong>given property-name</strong> (data AND gui ) at the <strong>window object</strong>. Then exposes data as state.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>useDatastream</strong> will request <strong>given datastream</strong> on <strong>given gams-object</strong>.  (default: current object + \"APP_DATA\" datastream)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Try to prefer useJsGlobal over useDatastream because of complexity.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<deckgo-highlight-code ts  terminal=\"none\" theme=\"one-light\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">\r\nconst GamsHooksDemo: React.FC = () =&gt; {\r\n\r\n  // hook returns data and gui prop of global variable.\r\n  // define type of returned property via ts\r\n  const { data, gui }: {data: string, gui: string} = useJsGlobal(&quot;demo_conf&quot;);\r\n\r\n  // use datastream works the same (awaits global json at a gams-object)\r\n  // empty will request current pid object\r\n  const dsData = useDatastream();\r\n  \r\n  // configure via params\r\n  const dsData2 = useDatastream(&quot;context:fercan&quot;);  // requests default datastream APP_DATA\r\n  const dsData3 = useDatastream(&quot;context:fercan&quot;, &quot;MY_DATASTREAM_NAME&quot;);\r\n  //       \r\n\r\n  // example for requesting different datastreams depending on object.\r\n  // assign datastream name as second param - do conditional logic to provide name.\r\n  const example = useDatastream(null, window.location.href.includes(&quot;mode_main&quot;) ? &quot;MAIN_DATASTREAM&quot; : &quot;SECONDARY_DATASTREAM&quot;);\r\n  // use returned values.\r\n  return (\r\n    &lt;div&gt;\r\n      {data ? &lt;p&gt;Data applied!&lt;/p&gt; : null}\r\n      &lt;p&gt;{data}&lt;/p&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n  )\r\n};\r\n\r\nexport default GamsHooksDemo;\r\n</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h3 id=\"usesolr\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#usesolr\" aria-label=\"usesolr permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useSolr</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>requests data, exposes state and basic functionality</strong> for handling <strong>Apache SOLR</strong> in GAMS context.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>requires the <strong>default configuration</strong> of Apache SOLR</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>First argument: URL of my exposed SOLR endpoint -> defaults to \"<a href=\"http://gams.uni-graz.at/pardus/search/select\">http://gams.uni-graz.at/pardus/search/select</a>\"</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Second argument: Predefine <strong>facets</strong> and initial <strong>facet fields</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<deckgo-highlight-code ts  terminal=\"none\" theme=\"one-light\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">\r\n// import of hook (could also import types from here)\r\nimport { useSolr } from &quot;zim-gamshooks&quot;;\r\n\r\nconst Demo: React.FC = () =&gt; {\r\n\r\n  // call and use exposed properties.\r\n  const { \r\n    // method to toggle facet fields\r\n    toggleFacetField,\r\n    // (= &quot;search-json&quot;) solr returned facet-fields and counts\r\n    facetFields,\r\n    // solr result \r\n    // (= &quot;result-json&quot;)\r\n    result,\r\n    // ref(!) \r\n    facetQueryObject \r\n    } = useSolr(&quot;https://my-solr-endpoint.org/search?&quot;, {&quot;dc_type&quot;: [], &quot;dct_medium&quot;: [], &quot;edm_agent&quot;: []});\r\n\r\n  return &lt;p&gt;SOLR demo component&lt;/p&gt;\r\n}\r\n\r\n</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h1 id=\"contribute\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contribute\" aria-label=\"contribute permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contribute</h1>\n<h2 id=\"useful-resources\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#useful-resources\" aria-label=\"useful resources permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Useful Resources</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/@jchiam/publishing-a-typescript-react-component-to-npm-d3cc15b8d0a2\">https://medium.com/@jchiam/publishing-a-typescript-react-component-to-npm-d3cc15b8d0a2</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://itnext.io/step-by-step-building-and-publishing-an-npm-typescript-package-44fe7164964c\">https://itnext.io/step-by-step-building-and-publishing-an-npm-typescript-package-44fe7164964c</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"create-react-app-and-useful-stuff\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#create-react-app-and-useful-stuff\" aria-label=\"create react app and useful stuff permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Create react app and useful stuff:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wmonk/create-react-app-typescript/blob/master/template/README.md#publishing-components-to-npm\">https://github.com/wmonk/create-react-app-typescript/blob/master/template/README.md#publishing-components-to-npm</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"important-scripts\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#important-scripts\" aria-label=\"important scripts permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hid